    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Trim the green stalk[s] off your<strong> aubergine[s]</strong> and slice, lengthways into bite-sized wedges</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/salt-and-chilli-pepper-aubergine-with-soy-longevity-noodles/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped aubergine</strong> to a large heat-proof bowl covered with <strong>cling film</strong></p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 4-5 min or until tender</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4 or more? Microwave for 6-8 min!</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/salt-and-chilli-pepper-aubergine-with-soy-longevity-noodles/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>cornflour </strong>to a small bowl with your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>ketjap manis</strong>, <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong>, <strong>mirin </strong>and <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong></p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>soy noodle sauce</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/salt-and-chilli-pepper-aubergine-with-soy-longevity-noodles/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>medium egg noodles</strong> and <strong>sweet pea pods<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>to a pot and cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> until fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 5-6 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain and return everything to the pot, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy noodle water</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/salt-and-chilli-pepper-aubergine-with-soy-longevity-noodles/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>microwaved aubergine </strong>and cook for 5-6 min or until browned</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/salt-and-chilli-pepper-aubergine-with-soy-longevity-noodles/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once browned add your <strong>cashews</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Once toasted add your <strong>salt & chilli pepper seasoning </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Give everything a good mix up until fully coated \u2013 this is your <strong>salt & chilli pepper aubergine</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/salt-and-chilli-pepper-aubergine-with-soy-longevity-noodles/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the noodles are cooked, add the <strong>soy noodle sauce </strong>to the pot and give everything a good mix up or until fully coated \u2013 this is your <strong>soy longevity noodles</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy noodle water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/salt-and-chilli-pepper-aubergine-with-soy-longevity-noodles/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>soy longevity noodles </strong>with the <strong>salt & chilli pepper aubergine </strong>on top</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
